                                    </span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="d-flex justify-content-between">
                                    <strong>Danh mục:</strong>
                                    <span>@Model.CategoryMotel.Type</span>
                                </li>
                                <li class="d-flex justify-content-between">
                                    <strong>Ngày đăng: </strong>
